00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:39,270
Hello.

358
00:17:39,314 --> 00:17:40,580
May I make an appointment with

359
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:42,200
specialists in the Neurology Department?

360
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:44,142
Their schedules are full
until next month.

361
00:17:44,171 --> 00:17:46,000
