362
00:17:46,485 --> 00:17:47,230
That's available.

363
00:17:47,257 --> 00:17:48,590
Do you have a pre-examination form?

364
00:17:49,285 --> 00:17:50,270
A pre-examination form?

365
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:51,950
Get a pre-examination form.

366
00:17:51,950 --> 00:17:53,542
Come back and queue after that.

367
00:17:55,100 --> 00:17:56,310
Sorry about this.

368
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:57,650
I've been queuing for a long time.

369
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,020
Can you please make an exception?

370
00:17:59,030 --> 00:17:59,950
That's the rule here.

371
00:18:00,100 --> 00:18:00,710
Next.

372
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:02,030
Can you hurry up?

373
00:18:02,114 --> 00:18:03,510
You need to get a pre-examination.

374
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:04,380
Why are you here

375
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:05,790
if you don't even know about that?

376
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:07,990
Miss, don't be impatient.

377
00:18:08,710 --> 00:18:10,360
The counter is over there.

378
00:18:10,470 --> 00:18:11,860
Go and take a number.

379
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:12,620
It'll be quick.

380
00:18:12,710 --> 00:18:13,514
It won't take long.

381
00:18:13,580 --> 00:18:14,100
Go now.

382
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:15,180
Don't be impatient.

383
00:18:15,270 --> 00:18:16,030
Thank you.

384
00:18:19,580 --> 00:18:21,070
Excuse me. Please make way. Thank you.

385
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:22,270
What do you need?

386
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:23,580
A number of Neurology Department.

387
00:18:23,580 --> 00:18:24,742
The Neurology Department?

388
00:18:25,085 --> 00:18:26,140
Come back in the afternoon.

389
00:18:26,150 --> 00:18:27,550
- In the afternoon?
- That's right.

390
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:28,620
- Next.
- Not now?

391
00:18:28,620 --> 00:18:29,420
No.

392
00:18:29,550 --> 00:18:29,990
Next.

393
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,740
- What do you need?

394
00:18:30,900 --> 00:18:31,860
Stomachache, right?

395
00:18:33,085 --> 00:18:34,130
Come back in the afternoon.

396
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:35,270
- Excuse me.
- Next.

397
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:38,470
Here.

398
00:18:48,060 --> 00:19:01,060
