399
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:06,340
Miss,

400
00:19:06,350 --> 00:19:07,810
which specialist are you trying to see?

401
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:08,660
What do you mean?

402
00:19:08,670 --> 00:19:10,370
Which specialist you're trying to see?

403
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:11,685
You want to make an appointment?

404
00:19:11,950 --> 00:19:12,857
Make an appointment?

405
00:19:13,100 --> 00:19:14,070
Yeah.

406
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:16,610
Which one? The Orthopedics Department?
Or the Oncology Department?

407
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:17,180
What?

408
00:19:17,714 --> 00:19:19,085
So, you're from another state, huh?

409
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:20,257
You couldn't understand me?

410
00:19:20,285 --> 00:19:22,457
I was asking you
which specialist you're trying to see.

411
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:23,828
Is it the Orthopedics Department?

412
00:19:24,228 --> 00:19:25,400
The Oncology Department?

413
00:19:25,410 --> 00:19:27,170
Internal Medicine or Surgery Department?

414
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:28,180
The Neurology Department.

415
00:19:28,190 --> 00:19:29,270
I need a number of it.

416
00:19:29,340 --> 00:19:31,030
No way, alright?

417
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:33,220
How about the Oncology Department?

418
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:36,420
Listen, I'm great friends with the head
of the Oncology Department.

419
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,820
I'll give you a discount, okay?

420
00:19:39,470 --> 00:19:40,340
No thanks.

421
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:48,270
Hello?

422
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:50,100
Guo, did you manage
to make an appointment?

423
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:51,428
No.

424
00:19:51,457 --> 00:19:53,980
I have to wait until next month
to make an appointment online.

425
00:19:53,990 --> 00:19:55,080
I'm at the hospital now.

426
00:19:55,380 --> 00:19:56,990
I can't get an appointment here as well.

427
00:19:57,420 --> 00:19:58,030
Guo,

428
00:19:58,230 --> 00:19:59,510
can you be flexible for once?

429
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:00,990
If this hospital doesn't work out,

430
00:20:00,990 --> 00:20:02,170
we can find another hospital

431
00:20:02,180 --> 00:20:03,200
and get another doctor.

432
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:05,580
Didn't you say you wanted
to see the best doctor here?

433
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:07,390
The Neurology Department
in Hospital Ruihua

434
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:08,990
is the best in Shanghai.

435
00:20:09,620 --> 00:20:10,180
Ms. Liu,

436
00:20:10,457 --> 00:20:11,885
please change my father's dressing.

437
00:20:11,890 --> 00:20:12,790
He was sweating profusely

438
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:13,950
- the entire night.
- Hello?

439
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:14,790
He didn't sleep well.

440
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:15,820
- Okay.
- Hello, Yu Jian?

441
00:20:15,820 --> 00:20:16,900
Did you hear me?

442
00:20:17,580 --> 00:20:18,300
Hello?

443
00:20:18,620 --> 00:20:20,950
Guo, I was talking to
the nurse just now.

444
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,270
As I was saying,

445
00:20:22,485 --> 00:20:23,530
since you're in Shanghai,

446
00:20:23,542 --> 00:20:25,000
can you think of something for me?

447
00:20:25,057 --> 00:20:26,771
I'm thinking of something right now.

448
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:28,340
It's not like you can get an appointment

449
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:30,030
with specialists in Shanghai
anytime you want.

450
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:31,420
I don't own the hospital.

451
00:20:31,430 --> 00:20:34,280
Can you not make it as if you're
dealing with official matters here?

452
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:35,620
I'm begging you here.

453
00:20:35,620 --> 00:20:37,142
Can't you please do something about it?

454
00:20:37,420 --> 00:20:38,620
You could've told me directly

455
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:40,660
if you don't wish to do it
or if you can't do it.

456
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:44,230
Yu Jian, I worked overtime last night
and skipped dinner

457
00:20:44,230 --> 00:20:46,610
just so I could come to the hospital.
But you're saying that?

458
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:47,270
That's right!

459
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:48,180
I can't do this!

460
00:20:48,257 --> 00:20:50,371
Come here and do it yourself
if you're that capable!

461
00:21:06,660 --> 00:21:07,620
Hello, Miss.

462
00:21:07,820 --> 00:21:10,020
Today's our grand opening.
Our set lunch has a discount.

463
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,180
Do you wish to know more?

464
00:21:11,950 --> 00:21:13,070
Do you have single sets?

465
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:13,820
Yes.

466
00:21:14,070 --> 00:21:15,990
We provide many promotional set lunches.

467
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,260
(Hongkong Plaza)
Please look.

468
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:19,900
(138 Yuan Set Lunch)
For example, our steak is popular.

469
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:22,070
We're giving discounts
because it's our grand opening.

470
00:21:22,070 --> 00:21:23,580
It costs 188 yuan on normal days.

471
00:21:24,580 --> 00:21:25,470
Forget about the steak.

472
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:26,510
