Does it

473
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:28,270
cost 78 if I order
the spaghetti ala carte?

474
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:29,270
This is already

475
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:30,270
our cheapest meal.

476
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:32,180
It's just ordinary spaghetti bolognese.

477
00:21:33,620 --> 00:21:34,100
Thank you.

478
00:21:34,171 --> 00:21:35,030
It's right over there.

479
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:37,580
Hello, mister.

480
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:39,030
(Personal Credit Card)
It's our grand opening.

481
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:41,110
(Your monthly bill is 1,638.7 yuan)
We have discounts.

482
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,340
You may take a look.

483
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:44,380
Hello, Miss.

484
00:21:44,380 --> 00:21:46,660
Would you be interested in our event?

485
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:47,620
Please take a look.

486
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:49,510
Hello, mister.

487
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:58,540
(Hongkong Plaza)

488
00:22:32,980 --> 00:22:33,820
(Xue Yuming)

489
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:34,550
(Dr. Jiang.)

490
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:35,910
(He's a specialist in neurology.)

491
00:22:36,100 --> 00:22:37,790
(You can seek her help
in Hospital Ruihua.)

492
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:39,230
(I already spoke to her.)

493
00:22:39,380 --> 00:22:40,710
(Xia Guo)
(Thank you, Mr. Xue.)

494
00:23:14,942 --> 00:23:16,860
(Yu Jian)
(Hello. The number you have dialed)

495
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,070
(is currently busy.)

496
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,340
(Please try again later.)

497
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:24,070
(At this moment,)

498
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:26,380
(I just wish to return to your side)

499
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:28,180
(and embrace you.)

500
00:23:29,171 --> 00:23:31,470
(However, such simple moments
of happiness in the past)

501
00:23:32,230 --> 00:23:33,990
(are quite a difficult task now.)

502
00:23:35,660 --> 00:23:37,790
(The distance between us
obstructed our relationship.)

503
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:40,140
(Our love was within reach,)

504
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:42,900
(but now, it's out of reach.)

505
00:23:58,820 --> 00:23:59,660
Who's there?

506
00:24:00,990 --> 00:24:01,710
Ms. Wang?

507
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:05,030
Ms. Wang!

508
00:24:11,171 --> 00:24:12,571
Who are you guys looking for?

509
00:24:12,820 --> 00:24:15,580
Ms. Wang told us to come here
to sign the rental agreement.

510
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:17,900
Wang Yan.

511
00:24:18,142 --> 00:24:19,400
Isn't this Wang Yan's house?

512
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:20,420
It's Unit 502.

513
00:24:20,470 --> 00:24:21,420
Coming.

514
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:22,660
Ms. Wang, you're here.

515
00:24:22,820 --> 00:24:23,620
What's going on?

516
00:24:23,750 --> 00:24:24,420
Sorry about that.

517
00:24:24,430 --> 00:24:25,270
I was stuck in a jam.

518
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:26,510
Sorry for being late.

519
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:29,820
