520
00:24:31,140 --> 00:24:32,580
Guys, please wait here.

521
00:24:35,660 --> 00:24:36,340
You?

522
00:24:36,660 --> 00:24:37,340
What's going on?

523
00:24:37,950 --> 00:24:39,510
Tell your tenants to leave.

524
00:24:39,950 --> 00:24:40,710
Answer me first.

525
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:41,850
Why didn't you go to Shanghai?

526
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:42,900
This is my personal matter.

527
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,420
How could you rent my unit out

528
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:45,510
without my permission?

529
00:24:45,860 --> 00:24:47,420
I thought you went to Shanghai.

530
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:49,114
The unit is vacant anyway.

531
00:24:49,115 --> 00:24:50,620
If I rent it out, we'll get extra money.

532
00:24:50,620 --> 00:24:51,710
Isn't that pretty good?

533
00:24:52,257 --> 00:24:53,310
Let me ask you something.

534
00:24:53,470 --> 00:24:55,470
Did you not go to Shanghai
because Zhang Xiaoqin

535
00:24:55,542 --> 00:24:56,950
