536
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,420
Forget about them.

537
00:24:58,420 --> 00:25:00,228
Let's deal with
the current situation first.

538
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:01,420
Girl,

539
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,900
why are you so silly?

