00:25:04,230 --> 00:25:06,742
How could you forsake
such an opportunity to move to Shanghai?

542
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:08,510
How many times have I told you this?

543
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:10,550
You must always prioritize yourself.

544
00:25:10,571 --> 00:25:11,790
You have to consider the life

545
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:12,990
you wish to lead in the future.

546
00:25:13,057 --> 00:25:14,180
Just because he stays here?

547
00:25:14,310 --> 00:25:15,230
Forget about it.

548
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:16,514
They're still waiting outside.

549
00:25:16,571 --> 00:25:17,380
That's why I suggest

550
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:18,900
you return to Shanghai first.

551
00:25:19,900 --> 00:25:21,900
What were you guys bickering about?

552
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:23,290
Ms. Wang, what exactly is going on?

553
00:25:23,342 --> 00:25:24,140
I'll be done.

554
00:25:24,420 --> 00:25:25,270
Give me a second.

555
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:28,230
Baby girl, I'm begging you here.

556
00:25:28,230 --> 00:25:29,340
Listen to me, okay?

557
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,342
I'll buy a flight ticket
for you right now.

558
00:25:31,542 --> 00:25:32,828
I'll take you to the airport now.

559
00:25:32,950 --> 00:25:34,550
Your future is more important.

560
00:25:34,914 --> 00:25:36,550
More like your profit is more important.

561
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:38,620
You want to chase me out

562
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:40,300
so that you can
make your rental income.

563
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:42,100
Of course I'll make my rental income.

564
00:25:42,620 --> 00:25:43,230
However,

565
00:25:43,230 --> 00:25:45,030
your future is my priority.

566
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:45,860
It's your career.

567
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,550
You do make it sound good, huh?

568
00:25:47,571 --> 00:25:49,580
Since when have you considered
my feelings since young?

569
00:25:49,580 --> 00:25:51,510
How could you be so heartless?

570
00:25:51,857 --> 00:25:53,510
Did you grow up on morning dew alone?

571
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:55,860
Have you not spent
a single cent of my money?

572
00:25:56,100 --> 00:25:57,140
Money, money, money.

573
00:25:57,140 --> 00:25:57,860
It's money again.

574
00:25:58,070 --> 00:25:59,790
Money is the only thing you talk about.

575
00:26:00,660 --> 00:26:01,380
Stop arguing.

576
00:26:01,520 --> 00:26:02,750
My child needs a quiet place.

577
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,310
Your mother

578
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:10,620
rented out your unit already?

579
00:26:11,742 --> 00:26:13,860
What will you guys do?
Where will you guys live?

580
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,750
I'll discuss it with Yu Jian after this.

581
00:26:20,270 --> 00:26:21,750
Don't blame me for criticizing you.

582
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:24,180
It's too impulsive for you

583
00:26:24,485 --> 00:26:26,030
to change your mind and stay here now.

584
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,860
Ms. Ping, I know that.

585
00:26:29,028 --> 00:26:31,030
But Yu Jian needs me the most
during this period.

586
00:26:31,230 --> 00:26:34,100
I'll be too selfish
if I leave right now.

587
00:26:34,314 --> 00:26:35,800
You didn't see it for yourself.

588
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:38,950
He and his family were elated
when they knew that I wasn't leaving.

589
00:26:39,057 --> 00:26:41,000
This is just like
what your mother had said.

590
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:44,900
As your friend, I truly don't wish

591
00:26:44,990 --> 00:26:47,600
to see you join this small circle
and follow in my footsteps.

592
00:26:49,860 --> 00:26:51,140
A small circle is not that bad.

593
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:54,510
There's Yu Jian and you in the circle.

594
00:26:55,710 --> 00:26:56,510
I feel at ease.

595
00:26:57,114 --> 00:26:58,660
What were you guys talking about?

596
00:26:59,950 --> 00:27:00,820
Xia Guo.

597
00:27:02,171 --> 00:27:03,380
You're something else now.

598
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:04,750
You leave and come back

599
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:06,180
whenever you feel like it.

600
00:27:06,340 --> 00:27:07,750
Do you not know

601
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:09,030
where you stand now

602
00:27:09,100 --> 00:27:11,270
just because that woman in Shanghai
buttered you up?

603
00:27:13,685 --> 00:27:15,750
Ms. Chen was the one
who permitted the transfer.

604
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,790
And, I decided
to give up on the opportunity

605
00:27:17,950 --> 00:27:19,030
out of the blue.

606
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:20,340
You came here not long ago.

607
00:27:20,342 --> 00:27:22,200
I had no time
to update you about my situation.

608
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:23,140
Is that so?

609
00:27:24,470 --> 00:27:26,710
So, since you didn't
come to work for several days,

610
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:28,857
can I consider that
as you being absent from work?

611
00:27:29,820 --> 00:27:30,950
I have my own leave.

612
00:27:31,028 --> 00:27:32,170
According to the labor law,

613
00:27:32,180 --> 00:27:34,990
employees who have worked for more than
one year but less than ten years

614
00:27:34,990 --> 00:27:37,310
are entitled to five days
of paid annual leave, Mr. Wang.

615
00:27:37,940 --> 00:27:38,580
Not bad at all.

616
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:39,880
You're bringing up the labor law?

617
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:41,400
Have you applied for leave, then?

618
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:49,550
Mr. Wang, she already
applied for leave from me.

619
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:51,580
I forgot to report it to you.

620
00:27:51,710 --> 00:27:53,100
I'm so forgetful.

621
00:27:53,371 --> 00:27:54,230
It's my negligence.

622
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:55,790
Sorry about that.

623
00:27:58,420 --> 00:27:59,140
Fine.

624
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,550
Guo,

625
00:28:20,990 --> 00:28:23,620
are you printing the quotation

626
00:28:23,714 --> 00:28:25,950
for Xinghui Supermarket's
pre-New Year promotion?

627
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:27,030
Yeah.

628
00:28:27,510 --> 00:28:28,310
Let me do it.

629
00:28:28,428 --> 00:28:31,171
Mr. Wang told me to deliver these to him
so that he could sign them.

630
00:28:31,828 --> 00:28:33,420
I was the one doing this previously.

631
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:34,900
Precisely.

632
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:36,750
I don't know what Mr. Wang is thinking.

633
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:38,710
No one wants to do such a chore.

634
00:28:51,340 --> 00:28:52,140
Hello, Zhao.

635
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,140
When are you free?

636
00:28:54,150 --> 00:28:55,280
Let's have a meal together.

637
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:56,620
Shouldn't we do a follow-up

638
00:28:56,620 --> 00:28:58,285
on the project we discussed before this?

639
00:28:59,028 --> 00:29:01,380
Mr. Wang already told Liang
to do the follow-up with me.

640
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,620
Liang is right beside me.

641
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:04,390
Do you guys need
to speak with each other?

642
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:06,380
No need for that.

643
00:29:06,750 --> 00:29:07,900
You guys can continue.

644
00:29:07,971 --> 00:29:09,860
I'll hang up first.
I won't interrupt you two.

645
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:21,190
Why did you cancel all of my tasks?

646
00:29:22,142 --> 00:29:24,470
You were a candidate
selected by our HQ in Shanghai.

647
00:29:24,542 --> 00:29:26,950
You don't need to trouble yourself
over such trivial affairs.

648
00:29:27,150 --> 00:29:28,230
What should I do, then?

649
00:29:28,580 --> 00:29:29,910
Are you trying

650
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:31,540
to make me leave of my own accord?

651
00:29:32,085 --> 00:29:33,100
You said that yourself.

652
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:35,100
I won't stop you if you want
to find a better job.

653
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:36,710
After all, your value is different now.

654
00:29:37,990 --> 00:29:40,060
Mr. Wang, I just wish to remind you

655
00:29:40,060 --> 00:29:41,470
that my contract hasn't expired yet.

656
00:29:41,470 --> 00:29:43,190
Unless you wish to sack me.

657
00:29:43,190 --> 00:29:44,340
I may consider that.

658
00:29:50,540 --> 00:29:51,820
That crook.

659
00:29:59,257 --> 00:30:00,730
(Yu Jian)
(I'm at the entrance now.)

660
00:30:00,740 --> 00:30:02,257
(I'll wait for you to get off work.)

661
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:32,500
(I stayed.)

662
00:30:32,714 --> 00:30:33,870
(I'm going to run toward him.)

663
00:30:34,630 --> 00:30:36,150
(I'll never regret it.)

664
00:30:48,220 --> 00:30:52,260
(Outpatient Department)

665
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:04,020
Mrs. Yu.

666
00:31:05,630 --> 00:31:06,430
Guo, you're here.

667
00:31:06,870 --> 00:31:07,340
He's asleep?

668
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:08,230
Where's Yu Jian?

669
00:31:08,390 --> 00:31:09,430
He went to find his senior.

670
00:31:09,780 --> 00:31:10,540
Have you eaten?

671
00:31:10,870 --> 00:31:11,630
I have.

672
00:31:11,630 --> 00:31:12,670
How was Mr. Yu doing today?

673
00:31:13,457 --> 00:31:15,150
He was pulling a long face all day long.

674
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:16,670
I didn't know what was on his mind.

675
00:31:17,230 --> 00:31:18,060
He's asleep now,

676
00:31:18,485 --> 00:31:19,910
but he didn't eat much for dinner.

677
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:22,020
Where's Li?

678
00:31:22,430 --> 00:31:23,340
Don't bring him up.

679
00:31:23,485 --> 00:31:25,600
He applied for a half-day leave
because his relatives

680
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:27,060
were here to visit him.

681
00:31:27,820 --> 00:31:29,150
Now that he's gone...

682
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:32,390
Mrs. Yu, what's wrong?

683
00:31:32,540 --> 00:31:33,340
Are you unwell?

684
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,340
Have a seat.

685
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:37,470
I've been here the entire day.

686
00:31:38,300 --> 00:31:39,910
My blood pressure is rising again.

687
00:31:40,742 --> 00:31:42,020
I didn't bring my medicine here.

688
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,090
What about this?
You can head back first.

689
00:31:46,100 --> 00:31:48,457
I'll keep an eye on Mr. Yu.
I'll do the dishes later.

690
00:31:51,430 --> 00:31:53,260
Are you sure you can do it?

691
00:31:53,390 --> 00:31:54,390
Why not?

692
00:31:54,780 --> 00:31:56,230
I think Li will come back soon.

693
00:31:56,670 --> 00:31:57,500
You should head back.

694
00:31:58,142 --> 00:31:59,670
Your health is more important. Come.

695
00:31:59,885 --> 00:32:00,990
Here, let me help you out.

696
00:32:01,390 --> 00:32:02,100
Guo,

697
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:04,150
I'm grateful that
you didn't go to Shanghai.

698
00:32:04,390 --> 00:32:06,260
If not, there'll be
no one here to assist me.

699
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,740
Mrs. Yu, don't say that.

700
00:32:07,870 --> 00:32:08,500
Come.

701
00:32:08,971 --> 00:32:10,150
Let me send you downstairs.

702
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,700
- I'll hire a cab for you.
- No need.

703
00:32:11,710 --> 00:32:12,470
It isn't that far.

704
00:32:12,870 --> 00:32:14,100
I'm not that fragile.

705
00:32:15,230 --> 00:32:16,230
You shouldn't see me off.

706
00:32:16,571 --> 00:32:18,100
He'll panic when he wakes up and sees

707
00:32:18,100 --> 00:32:19,885
- that no one is in the room.
- It's fine.

708
00:32:21,428 --> 00:32:22,540
Sorry for the trouble, then.

709
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:23,580
No problem.

710
00:32:23,670 --> 00:32:24,670
I'll call him later.

711
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:25,230
Okay.

712
00:32:25,340 --> 00:32:26,390
I'll tell Li to return.

713
00:32:26,470 --> 00:32:27,260
Please take care.

714
00:32:27,390 --> 00:32:28,710
Tell me when you get home, okay?

715
00:32:39,820 --> 00:32:40,670
(Xia Guo)

716
00:32:40,670 --> 00:32:41,770
(I'm at the hospital now.)

717
00:32:41,910 --> 00:32:43,257
(You can focus on your work.)

718
00:32:51,060 --> 00:32:52,100
Mr. Yu, you're awake.

719
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:53,540
Guo, you're here.

720
00:32:53,990 --> 00:32:54,740
Mrs. Yu just left.

721
00:32:59,870 --> 00:33:01,390
Of all the times to leave,

722
00:33:02,028 --> 00:33:03,500
she just had to leave at this moment.

723
00:33:04,028 --> 00:33:05,150
Are you looking for her?

724
00:33:05,670 --> 00:33:06,500
It's nothing.

725
00:33:09,060 --> 00:33:11,710
Where's Li, the caretaker?

726
00:33:12,150 --> 00:33:12,780
He's not around.

727
00:33:12,857 --> 00:33:14,230
Just tell me if you need anything.

728
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:15,470
It's nothing.

729
00:33:18,710 --> 00:33:20,100
Guo, have you eaten?

730
00:33:20,100 --> 00:33:22,260
You should go
and have something outside.

731
00:33:22,260 --> 00:33:23,100
I've already eaten.

732
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:24,260
Mr. Yu, are you hungry?

733
00:33:24,340 --> 00:33:25,300
I'm not.

734
00:33:28,470 --> 00:33:29,500
You see,

735
00:33:30,580 --> 00:33:31,870
the ventilation here is terrible.

736
00:33:32,390 --> 00:33:34,060
You should go out and take a breather.

737
00:33:34,670 --> 00:33:35,870
Do you think it's stuffy?

738
00:33:36,100 --> 00:33:37,060
Let me open the windows.

739
00:33:37,150 --> 00:33:38,340
No... No need for that.

740
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:43,470
Go and get me some water.

741
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:45,150
Okay.

742
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:49,990
But your flask is full.

743
00:33:50,190 --> 00:33:51,430
I'll pour some water for you.

744
00:33:56,870 --> 00:33:57,630
Guo,

745
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:59,320
just stop.

746
00:34:00,230 --> 00:34:01,910
Aren't you thirsty?

747
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:02,710
Put it down.

748
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:03,870
You're back.

749
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:05,140
Li, you're back.

750
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:05,910
Great.

751
00:34:06,190 --> 00:34:06,820
Hurry.

752
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:07,870
Get it for me.

753
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:09,180
Guo,

754
00:34:09,350 --> 00:34:10,870
stay outside for a while.

755
00:34:11,470 --> 00:34:12,990
Hurry, get me the pot.

756
00:34:13,660 --> 00:34:14,430
The pot.

757
00:34:17,870 --> 00:34:19,680
I have to do the dishes.

758
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,180
Sorry for the trouble.

759
00:34:30,542 --> 00:34:31,950
(Yu Jian)
(I just saw your text.)

760
00:34:31,950 --> 00:34:33,470
(I don't know what time
I can return.)

761
00:34:33,470 --> 00:34:34,540
(Head back and rest early.)

762
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:36,270
I have something
to discuss with you later.

763
00:34:36,790 --> 00:34:38,790
It's fine. You can go ahead.
I'll wait for you.

764
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,020
Let me see.

765
00:34:43,750 --> 00:34:44,580
How did you get that?

766
00:34:44,830 --> 00:34:45,470
I'm fine.

767
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,260
I'm just too exhausted
for the past few days.

768
00:34:47,270 --> 00:34:50,100
I was giddy and I
knocked my head on the site.

769
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:51,660
Does it hurt?

770
00:34:51,828 --> 00:34:52,820
I'm sure it hurts, right?

771
00:34:52,830 --> 00:34:53,500
It doesn't.

772
00:34:53,571 --> 00:34:54,500
I've already dressed it.

773
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:55,700
I'll be fine by tomorrow.

774
00:34:56,310 --> 00:34:57,470
That was careless of you.

775
00:34:58,140 --> 00:34:59,140
I'm fine.

776
00:34:59,430 --> 00:35:00,270
Let me send you back.

777
00:35:02,270 --> 00:35:02,910
Okay.

778
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,470
- Let me put on my coat.
- Okay.

779
00:35:04,660 --> 00:35:05,350
Go now.

780
00:35:12,060 --> 00:35:15,050
So, I said I had something
to discuss with you

781
00:35:15,060 --> 00:35:16,500
this afternoon, right?

782
00:35:17,580 --> 00:35:18,470
Actually,

783
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:20,390
my mother thought...

784
00:35:47,390 --> 00:35:48,390
Did I fall asleep?

785
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:50,180
What did you say just now?

786
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:53,750
It's nothing.

787
00:35:53,857 --> 00:35:55,485
Why don't you spend the night here?

788
00:35:55,490 --> 00:35:56,440
No need to send me back.

789
00:35:56,440 --> 00:35:57,660
- No way.
- You can stay.

790
00:35:57,660 --> 00:35:59,170
I can't rest
if you go home alone.

791
00:35:59,180 --> 00:35:59,990
No, you're too tired.

792
00:35:59,990 --> 00:36:00,990
Let's go.

793
00:36:04,310 --> 00:36:05,140
Let's go.

794
00:36:13,870 --> 00:36:14,830
Wang Chang'an again?

795
00:36:15,580 --> 00:36:16,620
He actually bullied you?

796
00:36:17,470 --> 00:36:18,470
I heard from Ms. Ping

797
00:36:18,628 --> 00:36:20,750
that Wang Chang'an wanted
to bring a relative of his

798
00:36:20,750 --> 00:36:22,057
to the company to replace me.

799
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:23,220
He hates me

800
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,350
because his plan was foiled.

801
00:36:25,750 --> 00:36:26,750
It's all my fault.

802
00:36:26,942 --> 00:36:28,457
You had to suffer because of me.

803
00:36:28,540 --> 00:36:29,790
Don't say that again.

804
00:36:29,910 --> 00:36:31,470
I chose to stay here of my own accord.

805
00:36:33,870 --> 00:36:35,060
By the way, I heard

806
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:37,500
that it's costly to hire
a monthly caretaker.

807
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,220
It costs 2,000 yuan, right?

808
00:36:39,350 --> 00:36:39,990
Of course.

809
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:42,420
The wage of a caretaker
who takes care of many individuals.

810
00:36:42,430 --> 00:36:44,260
A one-to-one caretaker
is even more expensive.

811
00:36:44,270 --> 00:36:45,350
How could we afford that?

812
00:36:46,750 --> 00:36:49,140
I'm sure you guys spent a lot
when Mr. Yu was hospitalized.

813
00:36:51,257 --> 00:36:53,228
We never expected
surgery to be that expensive.

814
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:55,990
He has to go through rehabilitation,
